er \"[2]\". Also, include a [[hyperlink]] to an online (.PDF file) copy which any reader can now consult, whether to confirm that the correct title does not contain the two-word phrase \"Housing Price\" -- instead what it actually contains, is: the phrase \"House Prices\" -- or whether to read (all or \"part\" of) what it says in that source. Also include an \"archive\" URL, which will likely NOT tend to become a \"[[dead link]]\".", "article_title": "Housing_bubble", "pageid": 1972320}, {"revid": 1120863915, "parentid": 1117358269, "user": "\u0412\u043b\u0430\u0434\u0438\u043c\u0438\u0440 \u041a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0440\u0438\u043d\u043e\u0432", "userid": 29107383, "timestamp": "2022-11-09T06:39:30Z", "size": 22783, "comment": "Russian residential real estate 2020\u20132022 bubble.", "article_title": "Housing_bubble", "pageid": 1972320}, {"revid": 1141745372, "parentid": 1120863915, "minor": "", "user": "Joyous!", "userid": 69412, "timestamp": "2023-02-26T15:51:26Z", "size": 22754, "comment": "Removing link(s) [[Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Indian property bubble]] closed as delete ([[WP:XFDC#4.0.13|XFDcloser]])", "article_title": "Housing_bubble", "pageid": 1972320}, {"revid": 1148242768, "parentid": 1141745372, "minor": "", "user": "Explicit", "userid": 4842600, "timestamp": "2023-04-04T23:30:45Z", "size": 22722, "comment": "Removing link(s) [[Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Bulgarian property bubble]] closed as delete ([[WP:XFDC#4.0.13|XFDcloser]])", "article_title": "Housing_bubble", "pageid": 1972320}, {"revid": 1149921844, "parentid": 1148242768, "user": "Crisantom", "userid": 29242247, "timestamp": "2023-04-15T08:16:41Z", "size": 22685, "comment": "/* Housing bubble definition */ Wikilinks", "article_title": "Housing_bubble", "pageid": 1972320}, {"revid": 1158245349, "parentid": 1149921844, "user": "Thiestru", "userid": 7241332, "timestamp": "2023-06-02T21:17:19Z", "size": 22684, "comment": "/* Housing bubble definition */", "article_title": "Housing_bubbl